
Fact actor 
  Identified by String

Fact counter
  Identified by Int 

Fact evidence
  Identified by actor * counter


Physical repeatedly
  Actor actor
  Creates 
    evidence(actor,Count(Foreach evidence : evidence When Present(evidence)))

// auxiliary
Fact completed
  Identified by "true" 

Fact once-completed
  Identified by actor * completed

Physical once
  Actor actor
  Conditioned by
    !(Present once-completed())
  Creates
    once-completed()

